  "description": "Prerequisite: Level 2+ Warlock, a Warlock Cantrip That Deals Damage\n\nChoose one of your known Warlock cantrips that deals damage and has a range of 10+ feet. When you cast that spell, its range increases by a number of feet equal to 30 times your Warlock level.\n\nRepeatable. You can gain this invocation more than once. Each time you do so, choose a different eligible cantrip.\n\nFoundry Note\n\nUse the Increase Range enchantment activity and drag your chosen cantrip to the chat card to increase its range and append \", Eldritch Spear\" for easier identification.",
